data.description: Monroe County Missouri Mini Farm for sale! Located between Paris & Shelbina. 10 acres, 2012 home, 4 outbuildings, 1 acre pond, 2 silos & you can raise what you want! Level to gently rolling property is fenced & cross fenced with 2 Ritchie Drinkers. The outbuildings are ready for your projects & equipment storage. Of the 10 acres there are just under 2 acres being used for the home & buildings. 7 acres await your livestock, garden, or orchard. The home, built-in with an amazing floor plan. Split bedroom design, well drafted laundry room just inside the back door and around the corner from the built-in desk. 3 Bedrooms & 2 baths. Vaulted Ceilings in the great room, huge center island/breakfast bar with stools and the dining area all open to the kitchen & living areas. The cabinetry is extremely well done, timeless design! The master suite has a massive walk-in closet, & master bath with soaking tub & separate shower. 1400+ sq ft waiting for you to See It! Love It! Own it!
